title: Carlos Childe - More Nights Than Days [320kbps] [MP3]
description:

More Nights than Days is the second studio album of the songwriter and singer Carlos Childe.His distinctive voice and a thick, dark sound are the main features of this recording. Ten new songs from ballads that talk about heartbreak to a powerful R&B.

Genre: Urban/R&B: Traditional R&B

The best album I've heard this year. Give it a chance!
